    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "young woman.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Some days after Fred and Ingrid and Glenn had",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "left Vienna for Berlin, for a very short family re-union,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "the Co-workers received a letter from our Austrian",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "friend and Co-worker, Dora Bauer, who told us of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "lectures Fred had given in Vienna and Linz. She also",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "wrote that Fred had told her of two space people,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
