      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "that first evening - -",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "And going through Germany he had filmed a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "strange formation in the sky. It was on September",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
