      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "In February this year I received photostats of corr-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "espondence and some still pictures from the film",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "that Fred Steckling took whilst travelling by train",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "between Mannheim and Frankfurt, in West Germany.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "The stills he had obtained by photographing from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "the screen, he said. He did not dare have the stills",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
