      "text": "in the middle of the blue sky.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "The 23 feet of Kodakcolour film were taken out",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "of an open window of a speeding express train,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "Mannheim-Frankfurt, approximately at 11.40 a.m.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "My camera is an automatic 8 mm Revere power",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "zoom, 30 mm lens. The objects, which can be seen,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "look like white cigarettes on the motion-picture be-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "hind trees, railroad stations and powerlines, which",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "were flying by and blocking their sight on occasions",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
