    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 116,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 117,
      "text": "\"- We took Madeleine along so the 22 NASA off-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 118,
      "text": "icials could see G.A.'s and her film, too. They seem-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 119,
      "text": "ed to be quite impressed, but would not make an",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 120,
      "text": "open statement concerning the film, naturally. The",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 121,
      "text": "2 hour meeting took place in Building A.I. They",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 122,
      "text": "treated us very nice and seemed to know much more",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123,
      "text": "of what we had to show and tell. One thing they",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124,
      "text": "said, however, and that is concerning Dr. Hynek. His",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 125,
      "text": "swamp-gas explanations are nonsense, we were told.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 126,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 127,
      "text": "\"But despite the evidence of the 3 films they still",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128,
      "text": "would like to have more positive proof, we were told,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129,
      "text": "for it still does not prove these ships to be extra-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
